title: Bar.Hunters.S01E01
description:
Tom Powers helps big dreamers find the perfect location to open their own bar.

"One Big Party" - Location: Moonshine Whiskey Bar. Join the party with our Bar Hunters, as bar expert Tom Powers heads out to Tempe, Arizona where he meets longtime pals Ben and Lars. They're looking to open the bar of their dreams: a down and dirty All-American country bar -- complete with a mechanical bull. Can Tom find them the best location to permanently plant their party...without breaking the bank?
